      • isTextType

        public boolean isTextType(String dataType)
        Description copied from interface: MaryInterface
        Check whether the given data type is a text type. For input types (i.e. types contained in MaryInterface.getAvailableInputTypes()) that are text types, the synthesis methods MaryInterface.generateText(String), MaryInterface.generateXML(String) and MaryInterface.generateAudio(String) can be used; for output types that are text types, the synthesis methods MaryInterface.generateText(String) and MaryInterface.generateText(Document) can be used.
        Specified by:
        isTextType in interface MaryInterface
        Parameters:
        dataType - an input or output data type.
        Returns:
        type

      • isXMLType

        public boolean isXMLType(String dataType)
        Description copied from interface: MaryInterface
        Check whether the given data type is an XML type. For input types (i.e. types contained in MaryInterface.getAvailableInputTypes()) that are XML types, the synthesis methods MaryInterface.generateText(Document), MaryInterface.generateXML(Document) and MaryInterface.generateAudio(Document) can be used; for output types that are XML types, the synthesis methods MaryInterface.generateXML(String) and MaryInterface.generateXML(Document) can be used.
        Specified by:
        isXMLType in interface MaryInterface
        Parameters:
        dataType - an input or output data type.
        Returns:
        type
